{"id":"3512","name":"LINE Out Helper","tagline":"Forward a phone number to LINE Out","icon":"ios14 c4292093695 g59814","latest":"24892","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3>What's this?</h3>\n<p>'LINE Out Helper' helps to call by <a href=\"https://line.me/en/call\">LINE Out</a> by forwarding a phone number to it.</p>\n<p>You can make a LINE Out call without memorizing or writing down a phone number on call history, Contacts, a web page etc.</p>\n<p>This Shortcut is spun off from another Shortcut, '<a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/538\">Call with Prefix</a>'. Please check it if you are interested.</p>\n<h3>Configuration</h3>\n<p>At installation, register the calling code of the country you like to call.</p>\n<p>Whenever you like, you can change it through 'Customize Shortcut' in setting: in 'Shortcuts' app, tap the 3 dots button on 'LINE Out Helper' icon, tap the 3 dots button again and tap 'Customize Shortcut…'.</p>\n<h3>How to use</h3>\n<p>2 ways to use:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Via iOS Action Extension</p>\n<p>When sharing a contact or a text including a phone number via Action Extension, start 'LINE Out Helper' (tap 'Shortcuts' App and tap 'LINE Out Helper'). You can make a call to the number by LINE Out.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Just start</p>\n<p>Or you can just start 'LINE Out Helper' in 'Shortcuts' app or its Widget. It will present 3 options: to get a phone number from Contacts or Clipboard (if any) or to input directly. As well, you can make a call to the number by LINE Out.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>(Optional) To receive updates,</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/2066\"><img alt=\"UpdateHub\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8tugTDE.png\"></a></p>\n<p>Please also install 'UpdateHub’ if you like to receive updates of 'LINE Out Helper'.</p>\n<p>You can check for updates whenever you like by running 'UpdateHub' for yourself.</p>\n<p>Or you can also select 'Check for updates' option during 'LINE Out Helper' run in 'Just start' mode.</p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>3.2.0 - Jan. 30, 2021, 4:14 a.m.</strong></p><p>Fixed a bug around LINE Out API and refactored.</p>"}